text: Yusuf Hossain Humayun is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Barisal-4. ==Career== Humayun was elected to parliament from Barisal-4 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Yusuf Hossain Humayun
